#
# T1_jlm_elastic
#
# TALYS JLMB (jlmmode 0, default) elastic scattering on 120Sn at En = 10 MeV.
# Adapted from talys/samples/n-Sn120-omp-JLM/org/talys.inp.
# Adds outangle y and fileelastic y to produce angular distributions.
# jlmmode defaults to 0 (alam = 0.44, Eq. 11.47 standard).
#
projectile n
element    sn
mass       120
energy     T1_jlm_elastic.energies
jlmomp y
outangle y
fileelastic y
